{
  "id": "6a46c03a6f20b55ff436087f",
  "title": "箇条書きのインデントに縦線を表示するUserCSS（for 箇条書きのバレットをFontAwesomeにするUserCSS）",
  "created": 1783021628,
  "updated": 1783505205,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a46c03a6f20b55ff436087f",
      "text": "箇条書きのインデントに縦線を表示するUserCSS（for 箇条書きのバレットをFontAwesomeにするUserCSS）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021628,
      "updated": 1783023482
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c2740000000000e4515b",
      "text": "[UserCSS.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783022197,
      "updated": 1783022208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c1540000000000e4514c",
      "text": "中身は「[borderでインデントに縦線を表示するUserCSS]」をページ内の次のコードで書き換えたもの[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021909,
      "updated": 1783022884
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c14f0000000000e45149",
      "text": " > background で線を引いてあげると右寄りになるのは防げそうです [zk_phi.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021903,
      "updated": 1783022126
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c14f0000000000e4514a",
      "text": "  code:例",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021903,
      "updated": 1783021904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c14f0000000000e4514b",
      "text": "   background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--page-bg) 40%, #000 40%, var(--page-bg) 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021903,
      "updated": 1783021904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c2040000000000e45155",
      "text": "  なお、元のページのタイトル自体に「borderで」という実装指定が含まれているため、もしページごと流用するなら改題を伴うことになるが、それは個人的に心理的抵抗を覚えるので別ページとしておいた",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783022084,
      "updated": 1783025979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c0660000000000e4513b",
      "text": "　　　また、「[インデントに縦線を表示するようにした]」という別のページについては、単に日記ページから上記のUserCSSに関する（当時の）いきさつを切り出して保存したものとみえ、上記のUserCSSを改変したUserCSSを置いておく場所としては適していないと判断した",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021670,
      "updated": 1783023431
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03c00000000005e7fb1",
      "text": "　cf. [箇条書きのバレットをFontAwesomeにするUserCSS]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021628,
      "updated": 1783341013
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9fce0000000000b4f7db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783341007,
      "updated": 1783341018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9fde0000000000b4f7dd",
      "text": "2026-07-06 CSS変数`--indent-bg-alpha:`を導入",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783341022,
      "updated": 1783505191
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4e212f0000000000648a3a",
      "text": "　`--indent-bg-alpha: .15;`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783505199,
      "updated": 1783505205
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9fcf0000000000b4f7dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783341008,
      "updated": 1783341008
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c09f0000000000e45141",
      "text": " code:style.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021727,
      "updated": 1783022169
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9eb50000000000b4f7d8",
      "text": "  html {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783340726,
      "updated": 1783340736
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9ec30000000000b4f7da",
      "text": "    --indent-bg-alpha: .15;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783340740,
      "updated": 1783341695
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b9ec00000000000b4f7d9",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783340736,
      "updated": 1783340736
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb2",
      "text": "  .indent-mark {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb3",
      "text": "  \theight: 100% !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb4",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb5",
      "text": "  .indent-mark .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb6",
      "text": "  \theight: 100% !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb7",
      "text": "  \toverflow: unset !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb8",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fb9",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+1):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fba",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-1) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%); /* 色の指定 */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783341561
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fbb",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fbc",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+2):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fbd",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-2) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783341559
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fbe",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fbf",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+3):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc0",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-3) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783341557
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc1",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc2",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+4):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc3",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-4) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783340955
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc4",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc5",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+5):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc6",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-5) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783340959
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc7",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc8",
      "text": "  .indent-mark span:nth-of-type(6n+6):not(:nth-last-child(1)):not(:nth-last-child(2)) .pad {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fc9",
      "text": "  \tbackground: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 40%, hsl(from var(--li-color-0) h s l / var(--indent-bg-alpha, 1)) 40%, transparent 50%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783340963
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46c03d00000000005e7fca",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783021630,
      "updated": 1783021630
    },
